As Tremor flew on he made it to the ocean and continued over it for 
the islands that would be known as Japan.  

JetV continued through the brush.  Answering Artemis he said "We 
have to follow Tremor to thier base, they no where are's is, so we 
must find thiers."  he said but just then as he flew out of the trees 
and off the edge of a cliff that hurled him towards the watery depths 
below.  Showing fright for a second he yelled "Stoppppp 
AAARRTEMIS" then, almost gracefully, he flipped over, his wheels 
folding in and his front coning.  As he hit the waer he went under 
then flew back out skipping along the water in his JetSki mode.  
His colors blended him into the water he was riding on.  He could 
clearly see Tremor flying above him.
